Note: Runa AI Framework - Advanced Voting Mechanism Systems
Competitive with democratic voting systems, corporate governance platforms, and blockchain voting protocols
Production-grade voting mechanisms with cryptographic security and tamper-proof verification :End Note

Note: Core voting mechanism types for democratic decision-making and consensus building
Type called "VotingMechanism":
    "simple_majority",
    "qualified_majority",
    "supermajority",
    "ranked_choice",
    "approval_voting",
    "score_voting",
    "borda_count",
    "condorcet_method",
    "single_transferable_vote",
    "quadratic_voting"

Note: Comprehensive voting participant with rights and authentication
Type called "VotingParticipant":
    "participant_id" as String,
    "participant_name" as String,
    "voting_weight" as Float,
    "authentication_status" as String,
    "eligibility_status" as String,
    "voting_history" as List[Dictionary],
    "delegation_permissions" as Dictionary,
