Note: Comprehensive voting election with governance and security
Type called "VotingElection":
    "election_id" as String,
    "election_name" as String,
    "voting_mechanism" as VotingMechanism,
    "eligible_voters" as List[VotingParticipant],
    "ballot_configuration" as VotingBallot,
    "election_timeline" as Dictionary,
